casebody.data:
FEDERAL NATIONAL MORTGAGE ASSOCIATION, ("FANNIE MAE"), a corporation organized and existing under the laws of the United States of America, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Judy LOWY and Myer Ziegelheim, Defendants-Petitioners. C-707 September Term 2018
082099 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000272-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
